  01 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  transcode-1.0.2-r2.ebuild, transcode-1.0.2-r3.ebuild:
  Remove build-time dependency on xproto and/or xextproto.

  23 Sep 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  transcode-1.0.2-r2.ebuild, transcode-1.0.2-r3.ebuild:
  Force dependency over latest versions of autotools, fixes bug #148706.

  26 Aug 2006; Hanno Boeck <hanno@gentoo.org>
  +files/transcode-1.0.2-new-ffmpeg, transcode-1.0.2-r3.ebuild:
  Add fix for latest ffmpeg.

*transcode-1.0.2-r3 (21 Aug 2006)

