*transcode-1.0.2-r1 (10 Dec 2005)

  10 Dec 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/transcode-1.0.2-bigdir.patch, +files/transcode-1.0.2-lzo2.patch,
  -transcode-1.0.1.ebuild, -transcode-1.0.2.ebuild,
  +transcode-1.0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump and removed previous 1.x versions. Close bug #110997 (modular
  x support, it's modular friendly saved ffmpeg that is still unfriendly), bug
  #111290 (missing libxml2 dependency), bug #112995 (long path crashes), bug
  #112382 (lzo-2 support).

